name: Women's 'Sanctity' Dress (red/silver)
description: Dress like a goddess in the 'Sanctity' dress, a tight fit that accentuates your divine features. A sharp V-neck cut is framed in a detailed silvery tattoo, providing a delicate tone to your appearance, while a solid black upper front on a blood-red background is extended to metallic lines over the shoulder, waist and trim, giving the impression that the wearer is armored with righteousness, beauty, and power.
